openHouses.notes: Twilight Tour! 86 Amherst Ave is a rare opportunity to own a multi-generational home on an idyllic, tree-lined street in a highly coveted ZIP Code. Sitting on a beautifully landscaped 9400 sq. ft. lot lies a spacious 3BR/2BA main house plus a detached garden suite. As you walk up to the front house, you are greeted by a charming covered porch that's perfect for lounging. On the main level, you'll find a spacious living room with gas fireplace, an adjacent dining area, a newly remodeled eat-in kitchen with quartz counters and S/S appliances, a family room that walks out to the patio, 2 generously sized BR's and a modern bath. There are many period details such as in-laid HW floors and crown molding as well as modern conveniences such as central A/C & Ring cameras. On the 2nd floor, there is an oversized primary suite with walk-in closet. The laundry/gym room is located in the basement. Through the lush courtyard, there is a 1BR/1BA garden suite with a living room, dining area and kitchenette. At the rear is a low-maintenance backyard surrounded by mature trees. Completing the home is a 2-car drive-thru garage with an extra large driveway. Can't be missed!
